{"tid":48268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿46歲母親改嫁　日少年剪刀狂插24歲繼父被捕","createTime":"2016-12-21T03:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T11:32:21.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05e540fc4a9be17b17f1aff101511cb38c5f115f","tid":48268,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】日本千葉縣一名46歲婦人改嫁給一名比自己年輕22載的男子，惟與前夫所生的14歲兒子與繼父一直關係惡劣，日前更以剪刀狂插對方的頭部，幸性命並無大礙。警方以企圖殺人罪拘捕涉事少年。<br />\n<br />\n　　警方指，被捕中學生周日晚上10時半在家中，向其24歲繼父施襲，先以殺蟲劑噴向其臉，再二話不說，掏出剪刀連番插向他的頭部。繼父雖然被捅多下，幸傷勢並不嚴重，兩星期可痊愈。<br />\n<br />\n　　少年的母親見狀後急忙報警，並指出「二人平時已關係欠佳」，警方循家庭糾紛的方向調查。"},{"pid":"d6923f657f76191289028f8b31ced99604d8e2fd","tid":48268,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"草食男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5078ec3a288645aa7b0a7b2ad5584065420d6e3","tid":48268,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"母控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3a61be4bab8830e8d0a980a771335040366853","tid":48268,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"繼父係咪啲日本mk呀<br />\n個仔頂唔撚順"},{"pid":"eaff6c4ec12dee42b8a76e80be266807d1294780","tid":48268,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>母控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四十路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c862ef23d1ea0301c5ba1a0f55ab7967007e3f9","tid":48268,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"媽媽是我的，不容別人搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fc40ac4be59c42463a235aa797bb6c2be0dbe5","tid":48268,"uid":37475